        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(cli): keep json startup output clean",
        "body": "Summary\n- Suppress central CLI startup progress when an invocation requests JSON output.\n- Require stdout to be TTY-safe before enabling Clack spinners, matching Clack's stdout default.\n- Add coverage for suppressing Clack spinners when stdout is not TTY-safe.\n\nTests\n- node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/cli/progress.test.ts test/cli-json-stdout.e2e.test.ts\n- node --import tsx src/entry.ts mcp list --json\n- node --import tsx src/entry.ts mcp list --json > /tmp/openclaw-mcp.json && python3 -m json.tool /tmp/openclaw-mcp.json >/dev/null\n- node_modules/oxfmt/bin/oxfmt --check src/cli/progress.ts src/cli/progress.test.ts src/cli/run-main.ts\n- node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs src/cli/progress.ts src/cli/progress.test.ts src/cli/run-main.ts\n- git diff --check\n\nCloses #88602\n",
